Program: Omnibus
Title: Up in Flames
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0376m3r
Last Broadcast Date: 22 November 2000
In 1996 Venice's opera house La Fenice was destroyed by fire. Author Michael Dibdin channels his fictional character, Venetian detective Aurelio Zen, to unravel the past, the present and future of La Fenice, Venice's Opera House.